{
  "stem": "3757.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we cannot be together because I have different paper than the child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when he would say once mommy or something, then we are lost both.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Said, no, no, I will take [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so they-- I thought, do you know somebody who I can trust and to go there?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she said, on-- in Buda, on a place-- they call it the Rose Hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was all villas-- there a beautiful place-- there is a woman who knows her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she knows the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I should go there and ask that she-- ask her to let me in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I-- it-- I cannot tell you the feeling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "First of all, I had to take-- I saw in the night to disappear Irene with my child.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know where they go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I know that she is in good hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This-- I didn't worry about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had to take the streetcar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have the star on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt like-- like a murderer or something, that everybody looks at me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody looked at me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had such a terrible feeling, like a criminal, because I am out without the star.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in an hour that I not suppose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the streetcar was sitting a woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were more people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And nobody paid attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But was sitting a woman, and in the window-- you know, the streetcar window-- I had the feeling that she is watching me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said, I don't get off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But one-- I had to go to the end stop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this woman left the train at stop before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she didn't-- this was only my feeling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to this woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a villa with a gate and a garden.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
